msgid ""
"The installer could not safely inspect the disk layout. Close the installer, "
"reconnect the storage device, and try again."
msgstr ""

#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:355
msgid "Do you want to proceed with the installation in EFI mode?"
msgstr "Ønsker du å fortsette med installasjonen i EFI-modus?"

#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:356
msgid ""
"The current boot is using EFI mode, but I did not find any EFI partition on "
"this computer. If this computer already has another system installed and you "
"intend to keep it installed, you will probably need to change the "
"configuration in the BIOS to boot in Legacy mode, also called BIOS mode."
msgstr ""
"Den nåværende oppstarten bruker EFI-modus, men jeg fant ingen EFI-partisjon "
"på denne datamaskinen. Hvis denne datamaskinen allerede har et annet system "
"installert og du har til hensikt å beholde det installert, må du "
"sannsynligvis endre konfigurasjonen i BIOS for å starte i Legacy-modus, også "
"kalt BIOS-modus."

#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:360
#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:375
msgid "Install the system"
msgstr "Installer systemet"

#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:370
msgid "Do you want to proceed with the installation in Legacy/BIOS mode?"
msgstr "Ønsker du å fortsette med installasjonen i Legacy/BIOS-modus?"

#: biglinux-livecd/usr/bin/calamares-biglinux:371
msgid ""
"The current boot is using Legacy/BIOS mode, but I found at least one EFI "
"partition on this computer. For the installation to be successful, you will "
"probably need to change the configuration in the BIOS to boot in EFI or UEFI "
"mode."
msgstr ""
"Den nåværende oppstarten bruker Legacy/BIOS-modus, men jeg fant minst én EFI-"
"partisjon på denne datamaskinen. For at installasjonen skal være vellykket, "
"må du sannsynligvis endre konfigurasjonen i BIOS for å starte i EFI- eller "
"UEFI-modus."

